  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159880/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765008687\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159880/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765008687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159880/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765008687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The time has come when people need your environmental orientation skills.<br><br>In this casual game, you will be the guide of several travelers who got lost and need to reach their desired destination. Unfortunately, you will not set a good example for others, but instead, you will help someone cross the street safely without being put at risk of being hit by a car.<br><br>Everyone is counting on you, and take care that no one needs unpleasant news in the city. No car is coming? Let's run away!<br><br>Game Features :<br>- 15 levels<br>- Heavy traffic<br>- Several groups of tourists",
  "about_the_game": "The time has come when people need your environmental orientation skills.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this casual game, you will be the guide of several travelers who got lost and need to reach their desired destination. Unfortunately, you will not set a good example for others, but instead, you will help someone cross the street safely without being put at risk of being hit by a car.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEveryone is counting on you, and take care that no one needs unpleasant news in the city. No car is coming? Let's run away!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features :<br />\r\n- 15 levels<br />\r\n- Heavy traffic<br />\r\n- Several groups of tourists",
